{"tid":1958936,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"正式成立學牌車牌繼牌苦主大聯盟","createTime":"2020-04-05T05:11:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T10:56:42.000Z","uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"91e2fcf97f97d9c1ea0120761f734492ed09ecf4","tid":1958936,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T05:11:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人地區議會手足做野但無人聲援點得</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200327/AGABHXLFE4NSAXIC3L4RONGK34/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200327%2FAGABHXLFE4NSAXIC3L4RONGK34%2F&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD8o9o6IkP5%2Bxjkbf63jgWy4%3D&h=7d8d0d3f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200327%2FAGABHXLFE4NSAXIC3L4RONGK34%2F&h=0d6ab0e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200327/AGABHXLFE4NSAXIC3L4RONGK34/</a><br />\n武漢肺炎蔓延，多個政府部門僅提供有限度服務。油尖旺區、沙田區、中西區等11個區議會交通事務委員會正副主席發起聯署，去信運輸及房屋局局長陳帆，要求政府自動延續駕駛執照有效期一年，以舒緩運輸署工作量。<br />\n<br />\n因應疫情發展，運輸署實施公務員在家工作安排，牌照服務及驗車服務都大受影響。由見及此，11個區議會交通事務委員會正副主席發起聯署，去信運輸及房屋局局長陳帆。聯署指，有不少快將到期的車輛車主無法在牌照屆滿前日成功續牌，由於到期的車輛不能合法在路面上行走或移動，而被迫長時間佔用停車格等，繼而引起泊位不足等的問題；也有商用車因車輛牌照未能順利延續而見財化水，甚至隨時因無法展示有效行車證而被警方抄牌。<br />\n<br />\n聯署強調，指局長是有權力行使權力，把今年1月起到年底前到期的65歲以下人士駕駛執照自動並免費延長有效期一年，以減輕運輸署牌照部工作量，集中力量先處理車輛牌照續期，並探討簡化無需驗車的車輛續牌程序，加快續牌效率。他們亦要求，若車主能證明，自己已在牌照到期前申請續牌，惟因運輸署暫停辦工引致未能展示有效行車證，警方應註銷告票。"},{"pid":"9ca7fdd22eabd34ddc3af124ee9b48dd62c08d0a","tid":1958936,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T05:13:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce62c333ba4fc41764e1ae05908386fa68040ada","tid":1958936,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T07:42:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60f8e4086baf9d693a350102d32361037feed25e","tid":1958936,"uid":201830,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T10:49:49.000Z","msg":"推 甩P甩左成個月 都味寄牌黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"950d4dd7fc9439f451882a57ff1a133f0fc344a9","tid":1958936,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T10:56:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}